snippet.title: Ammoru (1995) - Telugu HD Full Length Movie with English Subtitles || Soundarya | Ramya Krishna
snippet.description:
Watch Ammoru Telugu Full Length Movie with English Subtitles.Ammoru is a 1995 Telugu language Indian mythological fantasy film directed by Kodi Ramakrishna. The film was produced by Shyam Prasad Reddy under MS Arts Unit. The film stars Soundarya and Suresh in the lead roles with Ramireddy, Vadivukkarasi, Kallu Chidambaram and Babumohan portraying supporting roles.
